GET http://localhost:{{port}}/api/roles/permissions HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Crear rol
POST http://localhost:{{port}}/api/roles HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "code": "ADMIN-CLINICA",
    "name": "Administrador Clínica",
    "description": "Rol para administradores de la clínica con acceso completo",
    "permissionIds": [1, 2, 3]
}

###

### Crear rol de médico
POST http://localhost:{{port}}/api/roles HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "code": "MEDICO",
    "name": "Médico",
    "description": "Rol para médicos con acceso a historias clínicas",
    "permissionIds": [90, 91, 92]
}

###

### Obtener rol por ID
GET http://localhost:{{port}}/api/roles/1 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Listar roles (sin búsqueda)
POST http://localhost:{{port}}/api/roles/list HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "page": 0,
    "rows": 10,
    "search": "",
    "order_by": "r.nombre",
    "order": "ASC"
}

###

### Listar roles (con búsqueda)
POST http://localhost:{{port}}/api/roles/list HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "page": 0,
    "rows": 10,
    "search": "admin",
    "order_by": "r.nombre",
    "order": "ASC"
}

###

### Actualizar rol (reemplaza permisos)
PUT http://localhost:{{port}}/api/roles/1 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "name": "Administrador Clínica - Actualizado",
    "description": "Rol actualizado con nuevos permisos",
    "permissionIds": [1, 2, 3, 4]
}

###

### Activar / Inactivar rol (toggle)
PATCH http://localhost:{{port}}/api/roles/1/toggle-active HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Eliminar rol (soft delete)
DELETE http://localhost:{{port}}/api/roles/2 HTTP/1.1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###
